                            oc:textContent "**Problem:** The KMP library plugin produces a single build variant. There are no `debug`/`release` build types and no product flavors. Code that depends on variant-specific behavior, resources, or dependencies must be restructured." ] ;
                    oc:sectionLevel 2 ;
